!! Change role

Alter the role afterwards - `ALTER ROLE rast999 WITH CREATEDB CREATEROLE LOGIN REPLICATION;`

!! Set a new password

Setting new password is the same `ALTER ROLE sample WITH PASSWORD 'newpassword';`